{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@frozen"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TransitionPhase"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a view is appearing with a transition, the transition will first be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown with the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"willAppear"},{"type":"text","text":" phase, then will be immediately moved to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"identity"},{"type":"text","text":" phase. When a view is being removed, its transition is changed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"identity"},{"type":"text","text":" phase to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"didDisappear"},{"type":"text","text":" phase. If a view is removed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while it is still transitioning in, then its phase will change to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"didDisappear"},{"type":"text","text":". If a view is re-added while it is transitioning out, its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"phase will change back to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"identity"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the "},{"code":"identity","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" phase, transitions should generally not make any visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"change to the view they are applied to, since the transition’s view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifications in the "},{"code":"identity","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" phase will be applied to the view as long as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it is visible. In the "},{"code":"willAppear","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"didDisappear","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" phases, transitions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"should apply a change that will be animated to create the transition. If no"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animatable change is applied, then the transition will be a no-op."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See Also: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Transition"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See Also: "},{"code":"AnyTransition","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI"]]},"metadata":{"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore15TransitionPhaseO","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"TransitionPhase","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transition\/Transition.swift#L225","fileName":"Transition.swift"},"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Enumeration","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TransitionPhase","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"enum","title":"TransitionPhase"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenS